                "text": "Before I craft the perfect itinerary, I have a few quick questions to make it truly personalized for you! 🌟\n\n**Just need a few details:**\n\n1. **Travel Style** — Budget 💰 | Mid-range 🏨 | Luxury ✨\n2. **Interests** — What excites you most? (e.g., Shopping / Desert Adventure / Beaches & Water Parks / Fine Dining / Sightseeing & Culture — or a mix!)\n3. **Pace** — Relaxed 😎 | Moderate 🚶 | Packed & Action-Packed 🏃\n4. **Traveler Profiles** — Are all 3 adults of similar age group? Any seniors or differently-abled travelers we should plan around?\n5. **Dietary Preferences** — Vegetarian / Non-veg / Vegan? (Important for Dubai restaurant picks!)\n6. **Any must-dos or must-avoids?** (e.g., \"We MUST do the Burj Khalifa\" or \"No extreme adventure activities\")\n\n> 💡 **Quick heads-up on timing:** June in Dubai is **peak summer** — temperatures hit **38–42°C** ☀️🔥. The upside? **Indoor attractions** (Dubai Mall, Aquariums, Theme Parks) are heavily air-conditioned and **hotel rates drop significantly** compared to winter season. It's very much doable with the right planning — I'll make sure the itinerary is heat-smart!\n\nAlso, do you already have **flights and hotels** sorted, or would you like me to check availability for those too after the itinerary? 🛫🏨",
                "kind": "text"
            }
        ],
        "messageId": "74b02966-d45d-47a0-8680-0929cc782e07",
